Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:58.11,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,I've marked the towns and villages that \Nhave been attacked by the bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:04:01.71,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So they're showing up\N in unexpected places.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.71,0:04:04.86,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Must be so people won't figure \Nout where they'll show up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:13.39,sign_5964_101_Nean_Common_Real,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Nean\N{\fs24}Common Realm\N{\fs20}Kikka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:09.11,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,I've sent messages to the Magic Knights \Nin these areas to be on their guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.11,0:04:12.06,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,but that information \Nmight've also been leaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:15.25,main,julius,0000,0000,0000,,The bandits keep appearing in places \Nthat aren't heavily guarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:15.25,sign_6168_105_Heart_Kingdom,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Heart Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:20.60,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna have to figure out \Nwhere they'll pop up next,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:22.77,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,but that'll be tough to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:24.49,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's actually quite simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:25.62,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:37.60,sign_6449_110_Forsaken_Realm,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Forsaken Realm
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:37.60,sign_6449_111_Common_Realm,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Common Realm
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:37.60,sign_6449_112_Noble_Realm,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Noble Realm
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:37.60,sign_6449_113_Rayaka,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Rayaka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:37.60,sign_6449_114_Nean,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Nean
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:37.60,sign_6449_115_Kikka,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Kikka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:37.60,sign_6449_116_Raquey,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Raquey
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:29.30,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,First, we can rule out any place \Nthat's already been attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:37.60,sign_6499_112_Spade_Kingdom,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Spade Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:37.60,sign_6499_113_Diamond_Kingdom,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Diamond\N Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:33.32,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,The next likely targets will probably be \Nsomewhere a treasure's been found lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:35.90,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,or somewhere near a harvest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.60,main,Willaim,0000,0000,0000,,A bountiful one, specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:41.44,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Even then, that's more than \Nten or twenty places.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:45.45,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,We can probably rule out places that \Nare near the sites of attacks, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:49.35,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,They'll probably assume that such places \Nwill be on alert and harder to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:50.47,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Even then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:53.39,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,You think the two of us can't \Ncover so many locations, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:55.27,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,I know. That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:59.08,sign_7198_131_Nean,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Nean
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:59.08,sign_7198_132_Common_Realm,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Common Realm
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:59.08,sign_7198_133_Kikka,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Kikka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:04:59.08,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Here, and here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:02.43,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,And this village. \NCould you send out Magic Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:05.19,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,to these locations to be on \Nhigh alert for these bandits?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.19,0:05:09.09,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Why, though? If someone's leaking,\N there'd be no point—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.09,0:05:10.19,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:14.56,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You want to take advantage of the fact \Nthat someone is leaking information.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:18.95,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. They'll probably avoid places that \Nare being guarded by the Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:23.04,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,They'll prioritize places that \Naren't being guarded by the Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:26.38,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I-I knew that, duh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:28.93,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I was just testing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:33.41,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Which means the places they're \Nprobably going to go after
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:36.92,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,will be the town of Aymaia or Zocodany Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:38.12,sign_6168_105_Heart_Kingdom,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Heart\NKingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:10.15,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Yami and Vangeance
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.42,0:07:13.88,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,How are things looking over there, Yami?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:16.19,top,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing suspicious so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:16.89,sign_12339_133_Finnes_Calmreich,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Zocodany Village
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:18.96,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that an ancient magic item
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:21.89,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,was found in a cave near \NZocodany Village recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:23.92,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,That item is being regarded
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:27.40,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,as the village's treasure and is on \Ndisplay at the village elder's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:32.69,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Only a handful of Magic Knights \Nwould know about that at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:35.88,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early for the bandits \Nto show up for that treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:39.25,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,So if they show up in \Nsearch of that treasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:42.16,italics,William,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be clear that there's \Na traitor within our ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:45.17,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. How are thing looking in Aymaia?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:47.42,main,Willaim,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing suspicious here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:51.72,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,They just finished harvesting, and they're \Npreparing for their harvest festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:57.93,sign_12339_133_Finnes_Calmreich,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(1009,1)}The Town of Aymaia
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.19,0:07:54.68,top,William,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, their harvest \Nwas very good this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:57.62,italicstop,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the bandits would \Nlove to get their hands on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:07:59.30,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Just to remind you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.30,0:08:03.93,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where the bandits show up,\N don't handle them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:08.71,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wait until we contact the other\N and they arrive to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:09.55,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:10.94,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:15.77,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You better not go back on that just so \Nyou can get all the stars for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:17.83,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:20.45,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact you again if I see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:22.04,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:33.88,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,They actually showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:36.80,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, they're here, masked weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.65,0:08:39.26,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You hear me? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:44.40,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on? \NThis thing was working fine earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:47.54,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This ki...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:50.52,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Are they blocking the flow of mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:55.41,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're somehow \Nable to block comms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:58.03,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Guess they aren't ordinary bandits after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:03.54,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Must be a traitor from the Magic Knights... \NI'm gonna have to hunt them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:07.23,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like there are thirty... \Nno, more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.54,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,There are probably at least fifty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:14.49,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where the bandits show up,\N don't handle them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:16.80,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wait until we contact the other...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:20.80,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't get a hold of you, \Nso what the hell am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:22.85,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just gonna have to go on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:29.92,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cut them down before \Nthey get to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:32.06,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Cloaked...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:36.36,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Black Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:42.87,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy attack! Scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:48.41,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,0:09:49.33,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A Magic Knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:51.57,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some nerve, facing us alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:52.96,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna regret that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:58.72,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Magic: Dark Cloaked Lightless Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.67,0:10:03.61,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,That should take care \Nof about half of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:20.51,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:24.15,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've seen you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:27.09,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look like a Magic Knight, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:29.21,main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,You're the guy from that one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:31.67,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What one time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:36.79,main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,A few years ago, you got in the way of \Nus plundering that crummy little village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.79,0:10:39.38,main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I get to repay you for \Nthat sooner than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.22,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,A few years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:47.23,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You're the dude from that one time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:48.94,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I see now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:51.41,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Putting the guy's horrible \Nfashion sense aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:56.25,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,his magic powers aren't too impressive, \Nbut that staff is bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:59.19,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a treasure someone \Nfound in a dungeon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:02.56,main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think I'm the same as before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:05.53,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who gave you that staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:08.33,main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to know, \Nyou'll have to defeat me first!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:14.35,main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.89,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you guys for wasting my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.71,0:11:29.14,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:35.20,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have you spill who \Nthe hell gave you this staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.47,0:11:41.40,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Five... four... three...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:41.40,main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! I'll tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:43.49,main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:48.41,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Stay in your home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:52.91,main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Not another step, Magic Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:57.61,main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,If you move, this old bat is gonna get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.88,main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna pay you back a millionfold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:04.63,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,How? You think your buddies \Nstand a chance against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:07.93,main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,No, they probably don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:08.96,main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:12.27,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:17.80,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This magic—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:21.36,main,Mohl,0000,0000,0000,,It's a type of earth magic spell,\N Witch Hunter Claws,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:23.39,main,Mohl,0000,0000,0000,,you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:26.00,main,goht,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:29.74,main,goht,0000,0000,0000,,that's a binding spell \Ncalled Sheep Horn Snag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:32.61,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen you guys before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:37.51,top,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're Goht from the Crimson Lion Kings\N and Mohl from the Silver Eagles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:40.50,sign_18183_232_Silver_Eagles_Sq,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1003,1)\blur3}Silver Eagles Squad Member\N{\fs26}Mohl
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:40.50,sign_18183_233_Crimson_Lion_Kin,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1003,1)\blur3}Crimson Lion Kings Squad Member\N{\fs26}Goht
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.51,0:12:40.50,top,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we actually had two \Ntraitors instead of one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:42.61,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So you were the ones giving these bandits
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:47.13,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,magic items and information,\N and having them attack the villages.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:52.93,main,Goht,0000,0000,0000,,There's no use in struggling. \NNo man can break through that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:57.73,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are a disgrace to the Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:13:04.11,main,Goht,0000,0000,0000,,You're the foreigner named Yami Sukehiro \Nthat the Wizard King picked up, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:08.16,main,Goht,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the Wizard King was up to \Nsomething. So this is what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:12.83,main,Mohl,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that the \NWizard King's order to protect
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:16.51,main,Mohl,0000,0000,0000,,the villages in the area was a diversion
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:20.24,main,Mohl,0000,0000,0000,,to pinpoint where we'd attack next.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:22.92,main,Mohl,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we completely fell for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.43,0:13:28.41,main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Goht and Lord Mohl,\N you're amazing for figuring out their plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:30.99,main,Mohl,0000,0000,0000,,You go hurry up and find their treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:32.09,main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:36.00,main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, it was at the village elder's house,\N right? Hey, take me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.49,main,Old,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.49,0:13:38.83,main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,You men, follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:39.72,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:46.40,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights exist to serve and \Nprotect the people of the Clover Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:47.74,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you bastards...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:49.39,main,Mohl,0000,0000,0000,,We'll tell the Wizard King
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:54.08,main,Mohl,0000,0000,0000,,that we found you after you'd \Nbeen defeated by the bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:57.13,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think I'll go down that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:13:58.99,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you back a millionfold!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.99,0:14:01.47,main,Goht,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. Only a weakling would \Nsay something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:02.71,main,Mohl,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:10.51,main,Mohl,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you think he can hold out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:12.47,main,Goht,0000,0000,0000,,Just give it up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:15.38,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'd give up that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:18.80,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet... I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:21.44,main,Goht,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're just about at your limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:23.60,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell cares about limits?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:29.45,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just surpass them! Right here, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:43.42,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Dracaena Formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.84,0:14:54.08,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.24,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Took you long enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:56.97,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you know that I hurried over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:15:00.11,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,When I wasn't able to get a hold of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:04.86,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,I figured the bandits had \Nappeared in Zocodany.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:08.11,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:11.77,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm gonna pay it back quick, masked weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:13.78,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,They're the ones behind all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:17.49,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Goht and Mohl... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:19.55,main,Goht,0000,0000,0000,,William Vangeance...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:22.85,main,Goht,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you were following the \NWizard King's orders, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:26.29,main,Mohl,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to defeat you \Nalong with Yami Sukehiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.34,0:15:33.73,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:43.31,main,Goht,0000,0000,0000,,Attack of the Horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:49.98,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Cloaked Lightless Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:59.01,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I'd pay you back \Na billionfold, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:02.33,main,Goht,0000,0000,0000,,Please go easy on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:10.11,main,Mohl,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:15.18,main,Mohl,0000,0000,0000,,Let's negotiate. Why not join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:16.26,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:18.81,main,Mohl,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it'll be quite fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:22.88,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds tempting... But I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:25.69,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,I swore my loyalty to the \NWizard King, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:29.84,main,Mohl,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:40.53,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I already paid you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:45.05,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,It truly is unfortunate
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:48.87,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,that there were traitors \Namong the Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:57.93,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Now, all that's left is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:00.14,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.13,0:17:07.48,main,Boss,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who the hell \Nthat is, but take him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.04,0:17:14.76,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't planning on interfering,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:16.93,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,but I think I'm allowed \Nto have a {\i1}little{\i0} fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:24.83,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:28.50,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:34.26,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You were able to capture the traitors \Nas well as all of the bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:37.51,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... the bandits' boss was \Nout cold at the top of the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:41.51,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I guess weirder things have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:45.09,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Again, excellent work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:46.06,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.57,0:17:50.44,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Yami, Vangeance...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.12,0:17:53.29,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Considering everything you've done so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:57.44,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I'm appointing both of you \Nas captains of new squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:17:59.47,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're making us...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:01.70,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,...captains of new squads?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.67,0:18:03.95,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Will you accept my offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:11.73,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the competition to see who can \Nbecome squad captain first ended in a draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:14.50,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but our true competition \Nstill lies ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:15.45,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:16.99,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:17.97,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Neither will I.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:23.22,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in both of you. Yami, \Nwhat kind of squad will you create?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:26.31,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of squad? Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:32.14,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,A squad where status, bloodlines, \Nand social standing don't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:37.48,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll round up some outsiders and hooligans, \Nand create a place where they can belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:40.31,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you did for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.31,0:18:42.49,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. That sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:46.29,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call them... Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:50.59,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gather up a bunch of guys who all \Nhave their own color, mix them all up,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:53.01,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,and once their colors all mix together...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:55.95,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Black. The Black Hooligans?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:57.80,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, let's go with bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:19:00.51,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll call them the Black Bulls!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:02.49,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Bulls...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:04.90,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds perfect for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:05.85,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:08.75,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,I will create the Golden Dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:09.85,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The Golden...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:14.27,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Creating the ultimate squad is \Nmy way of repaying you, Lord Julius.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.91,0:19:15.88,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,As the name suggests,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:20.87,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,I will make a squad that will bring \Na golden dawn to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:23.65,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the night is dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:27.77,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,I will prove that the light will always shine,\N and a golden dawn will come one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:30.04,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,How cheesy can you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.47,0:19:33.85,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds wonderful, too.\NI look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:39.00,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, you are the Captain of the \NGolden Dawn. Congratulations, William.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:39.80,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:47.64,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,And starting today, you are the Captain of \Nthe Magic Knights Squad, the Black Bulls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:49.06,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Yami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:55.19,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Looking forward to working with you, Goldie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:01.69,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:03.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:05.32,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:08.76,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I guess you went through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:11.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So, what were you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.93,0:20:14.32,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you stumble, \Neven if you think you might lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:16.45,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be fine as long as you don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:18.36,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever give up in any situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:19.71,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Surpass your limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:21.75,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Then a path will always open up for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:24.80,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Quit being so depressed just because \Nyou lost to your rival once!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:27.97,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you lose 99 times, you just \Nhave to win the next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:32.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see... You should've just \Nsaid that in the first pla—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.43,0:20:33.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:36.19,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! You're going to crush my skull!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:39.87,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But Captain Yami's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:41.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in being depressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:46.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm gonna catch \Nup to Yuno and surpass him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:47.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.17,0:20:52.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,shouldn't we be getting the results from \Nthe Royal Knights Selection Exam soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:57.08,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, yeah... I-I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:21:00.27,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, messenger owls!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.71,0:21:05.72,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,The hell? That's no messenger owl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:09.77,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno who the hell you are,\N but stop that racket!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.77,0:21:12.35,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know that this is the \Nhome of the Black Bulls,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:14.52,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,the Magic Knights Squad that Mister Yami—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:16.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:24.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're Lady Sisgoleon!
