Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.00,0:23:01.95,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Weird Mask Guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.08,0:23:05.40,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Golden Weird Mask Guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:07.54,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather you didn't call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.54,0:23:08.34,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.34,0:23:10.27,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Baldie Weird Mask Guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.27,0:23:12.72,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather you didn't call me that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:14.69,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Baldie Long Drawers Mask Guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.69,0:23:15.97,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.35,0:23:18.44,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Baldie Long Drawers Belly Warmer Mask Guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.44,0:23:20.35,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't even make sense anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:23.36,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Baldie Long Drawers Belly Warmer \NTiny Mustache Mask Guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.36,0:23:24.73,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,How long is this going to go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.73,0:23:28.10,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Baldie Long Drawers Belly \NWarmer Tiny Mustache...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.10,0:23:30.84,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,who wears his shirt and \Nsocks backwards... Mask Guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.68,0:23:30.84,top,William,0000,0000,0000,,No, really. How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.84,0:23:32.48,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,How about Birthday Suit Mask Guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.22,0:23:39.08,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally time to find out the results \Nof the Royal Knights Selection Exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:41.87,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I know for damn sure that I was chosen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.87,0:23:43.58,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling worried?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.58,0:23:47.25,main,magna,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 87: \N"Formation of the Royal Knights."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.71,0:23:50.39,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 87\N\N{\fs18} Formation of the Royal Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.25,0:23:48.80,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fired up!
